headline: Onto Innovation (ONTO) Misses Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: Onto Innovation (ONTO) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -1.37% and +0.10%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
